# Custom Agents Directory
#
# Teams define custom agents here extending _base-agent.
# See sqad-method/agents/_base-agent.md for the base class.
#
# Example custom agent:
#
# ---
# extends: _base-agent
# name: Aria
# agent_id: custom-perf-lead
# role: Performance Engineer
# icon: "⚡"
# participates_in: [review, spec]
# ---
# # Aria — Performance Engineer
# ## Identity / Communication / Principles / Review Instinct
#
# /setup and /refresh scan this directory.
# Skills check participates_in to load per phase.
